name: Postcard from the Edge of the Galaxy 31/31 - Infinite Edition
description:
An alien vista evolves in this generative piece inspired by science fiction landscapes. Click or tap to reset. Made with p5.js.

This special edition generates a new random vista with each click or tap.

The piece starts in Auto Mode and will show a new generative vista every 60 seconds. Press the space bar to toggle Auto Mode on and off.
